    <span class="category-tag">Evangelism</span>
    <h1>The Miracle Question: <em>13 Words</em> That Open Any Door</h1>
    <p class="page-hero-desc">One question. Thirteen words. It works in any language, any culture, with any person — and it starts a Gospel conversation without pressure, arguments, or religious weirdness.</p>
  </div>
